data.description: Recently renovated multi-unit home with updated kitchens and bathrooms, lighting, basement, and flooring. The first unit is 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, the second unit is a 2 floor unit with 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. Home can be provided vacant for optimal cashflow or live in one unit and rent out the other. The utilities in the basement have had multiple updates. The house has plenty of space to fit all your needs and design ideas. Easy commute to NYC, Newark International Airport, and all highways and transportation routes. Close to shopping centers, myriad of restaurants to satisfy any appetite, and all the excellent universities and schools New Jersey has to offer. Make this your next home or add this to your investment portfolio. Schedule a tour today and place your offer!
